      • getElement

        public org.w3c.dom.Element getElement(java.lang.String elementName,
                                      org.w3c.dom.Document document)
        クラスからコピーされた説明: RTSProperties
        Pure virtual function for offspring classes. Return well build xml element object. createElement method appends only attributes (Map member). So, offspring classes must override this method and in this method, offspring class must manually append their child elements.
        定義:
        getElement クラス内 RTSProperties
        パラメータ:

        document - XML document object
